description:
Hear the inspiring story of how one man went from a death sentence as a convicted criminal to finding his life's purpose through the unwavering love of God.

This powerful testimony will touch your heart and remind you that no matter where you come from or what you've been through, God's love is always there to guide you towards your true purpose in life. Watch now to be inspired and encouraged by this incredible story of redemption and faith.
fulltitle: From Death Sentence to Life's Purpose Unwavering Love of God
